<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>

    .para,
    .greeting,
    .signature,
    #bh_logo_img,   
    .info,
    p {
      font-family: Geneva, 'Trebuchet MS', Arial;
      color: #222222;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 125%;
    }
    .signature {
      font-size: 110%; 
    }
    table.wrapper {
      width: 100%;
    }
    table.header,
    table.footer {
      width: 600px; 
    }
    table.content {
      width: 575px;
    }
    a {
      color: #222222; 
    }
    a#bh_logo_link {
      text-decoration: none; 
    }
    #bh_logo_img {
      font-size: 275%;
    }
    #bh_logo {
      height: 70px;
    }
    #bh_logo, 
    .info {
      border-left: 10px solid white;
    }

    .space,
    .divider-normal {
      height: 7px;
    }

    .contact {
      width: 140px;
    }

    .address {
      color: #bbbbbb;
    }

    .divider-normal {
      border-top: 3px solid #222222;
    }
    .divider-small {
      border-top: 1.25px solid #444444;  
      height: 13px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table class="wrapper">
    <table class="header" align="center">
      <tr>
        <td id="bh_logo"><a id="bh_logo_link" href="https://beehouse-library.herokuapp.com"><img id="bh_logo_img" src="http://s13.postimg.org/cef4nkub7/beehouse_pg_logo.png" alt="Beehouse Library"/></a></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="divider-normal" colspan="3"></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <table class="content" align="center">
      <tr><td class="greeting">Hey <%= @patron.name.split(' ')[0] %>,</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="space"></td></tr>

      <tr class="para"><td><p>Thank you for joining the Beehouse community. We currently have <%= @collection_count %> books in the system, and, if we can count on anything, we'll have more books in the future. Take some time to <a href="https://beehouse-library.herokuapp.com/books">look through what's there</a>. See if what you're looking for's there, or if anything unexpected catches your eye.</p></td></tr> 

      <tr class="para"><td><p>Feel free to let me know if there's anything I can help you with. This welcome is sent out from my personal email so you can reply directly, no problem.</p></td></tr>

      <tr><td class="signature">Cheers,<br>
      Clay a</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="space"></td></tr>
    </table>
    <table class="footer" align="center"> 
      <tr>
        <td class="divider-small" colspan="2"></td>
      </tr>   
      <tr>
        <td class="info contact" valign="top">
          Clayton Albachten<br>
          Beehouse Librarian<br> 
          T: <a href="tel:%28646%29%20787-5852" value="+16467875852" target="_blank">(646) 787-5852</a>
        </td>
        <td class="info address" valign="top">
          <br>
          5 E67th Street, Apt. 1B<br>
          New York, NY 10065
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>    
  </table>
</body>
</html>